# Top 20 Wedding Photo Booth Props

Based on an analysis of the most popular and best-selling physical wedding photo booth props (specifically high-quality PVC sets), here are 20 distinct trending ideas to inspire your stock prop line:

| # | Phrase | Visual Design | Shape |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| 1 | **Team Bride** | Elegant pink script font with a delicate floral border. | Rectangle |
| 2 | **Team Groom** | Bold, masculine block font on a navy blue or black background. | Rectangle |
| 3 | **Just Married** | White typewriter-style font on a rustic wood-grain background. | Arrow |
| 4 | **Best Wedding Ever** | Shiny gold glitter script font on a clean white background. | Circle |
| 5 | **I came for the CAKE** | Modern sans-serif font with a small wedding cake icon. | Rectangle |
| 6 | **He put a ring on it** | Hand-lettered playful style with a diamond ring silhouette. | Speech Bubble |
| 7 | **Happily Ever After** | Formal calligraphy font framed by a gold foil floral wreath. | Circle |
| 8 | **Drunk in Love** | Script font with a wine glass icon on a dark chalkboard style. | Rectangle |
| 9 | **Mr. Right** | Classy serif font accompanied by a black bowtie graphic. | Rectangle/Mustache |
| 10 | **Mrs. Always Right** | Elegant cursive with a bright red lipstick "kiss" mark. | Speech Bubble |
| 11 | **Finally!** | Large, high-impact block capitals with a silver foil effect. | Rectangle |
| 12 | **Party Crasher** | Yellow and black "Warning" sign style with bold block text. | Arrow |
| 13 | **Wifed Up** | Glittery gold font on a soft blush pink background. | Heart |
| 14 | **Still Single** | Retro neon-style font on a dark, textured background. | Rectangle |
| 15 | **Hot Mess** | Fun, comic-book style font with a jagged, colorful border. | Starburst |
| 16 | **I'm with Her** | Simple block font with a pointing index finger icon. | Arrow |
| 17 | **I'm with Him** | Simple block font with a pointing index finger icon. | Arrow |
| 18 | **Best Man** | Formal tuxedo-stripe design with a sophisticated serif font. | Badge/Shield |
| 19 | **Maid of Honor** | Delicate script font with rose gold accents and floral corners. | Oval |
| 20 | **I came for the BEER** | Chalkboard-style white font on a black background. | Mug Silhouette |

---

> [!TIP]
> **Key Wedding Trends Observed:**
> *   **Visuals:** Designs lean heavily toward **gold script**, **floral wreaths**, and **rustic wood** textures.
> *   **Tone:** Bestselling sets usually offer a strategic mix of "sentimental" (Just Married, Happily Ever After) and "humorous" (Party Crasher, I came for the CAKE) phrases to engage all types of wedding guests.
> *   **Material Focus:** The leading sets all highlight their use of **PVC or heavy-duty plastic** to assure buyers they won't bend or snap like cheap cardstock props.
